<h4 id="fifty-seven-minutes">Fifty-Seven Minutes</h4>
<p>On November 5, 2022, at 13:18 UTC, the domain <code>octra.org</code>
was registered through <a href="https://www.godaddy.com/">GoDaddy</a>
under <a href="https://www.domainsbyproxy.com/">Domains By Proxy</a>
privacy protection. The registrant’s name was hidden under “Registration
Private.” Forty-two minutes later, at 14:00:10 UTC, a GitHub user named
<a href="https://github.com/lambda0xE">lambda0xE</a> was created. The
profile would later read as follows:</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Section</th>
<th>Data</th>
</tr>
</thead>
